@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gagskm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = v1
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.abs(tmp + 0.29)))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.sin(v1 + 0.94)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.12 - v2 + 0.11)) * 0.68)
    v1 = v0
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.21)))
    v0 = ((tmp + wp.cos(v2 + 0.05)) / v2)
    data[tid] = v0
